    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels at MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ has been completed for geometric tolerances and the overall hemolysis predictions are within an acceptable range for engineering review. The assessment team considers the evidence sufficient to support a regulatory submission at this stage.",
